#  **Welcome to Jamin's Portfolio GitHub Page.**
Hi! On this website you will find out more information about me, projects I have completed, and general knowledge about software engineering and programming.  

## ** About Me**

I am a highly self-motivated Software Engineer with an background in computer science.  My mission and passion is using my creativity to build software to add value to individuals, organizations, and communities.  My main areas of interest include the entertainment, finance, and corporate industries.  I create SaaS to help these businesses grow and improve.  I am also a natural problem solver that enjoys the everyday challenges software engineering brings.  Learning is one of my favorite pass times. In addition to my traditional education, I have learned and continue to learn from numerous resources, books, and courses to hone my programming skills.


### ** Hobbies **
When I am not coding, you can find me at the beach with my beautiful wife and son!  I also enjoy hiking, writing, film-making, and last but not least..coffee!
